subject: Receive Your ATM Card From Fed
body:
Receive Your ATM Card From FedEx Office
 Ship Center St Louis Missouri, Mo, USA
FedEx Office  Ship Center
St Louis Mo, Mo, USA
Open until 9:00 PM
Contact: Stephen Lawrence via Email on (
onlincare90@aol.com
)
Dear Beneficiary,
The management of this company, wishes to inform you that, we received
a parcel containing an (ATM VISA Card)  for safety
delivery to your residential. This parcel was brought to us by the
Visa Card payment office of  Bank of America, 
please
reconfirm the below information to us to avoid a wrongful delivery.
(1) YOUR Full names............
(2) YOUR Parcel owner address......
(3) YOUR Country/State..............
(4) YOUR Cell Number...........
We will register your package and send you the tracking before we
proceed for safety delivery of your package as soon as you reconfirm
the required information’s for safety delivery, Contact the delivery
officer Stephen Lawrence on Email via (
onlincare90@aol.com
)
Please make a Choice of delivery for the FedEx Shipping and Airport
clearance charge of your (ATM VISA Card) as they are as charges
Below;
(1)24hrs/$150
(1)48hrs/$90
(2)72hrs/$65
FedEx Office is your local  company in St Louis Missouri,
offering a wide range delivery and self-service copying. Come and ship
with FedEx®.

subject: Re: Receive Your ATM Card From Fed
body:
Dear Office Ship Center,

I received your message regarding the delivery of an ATM VISA Card. However, I would like to clarify a few things before proceeding.

Firstly, could you please provide more details about this card? For instance, who is it from and what is its purpose? 

Secondly, you mentioned some charges for shipping and airport clearance. Could you please specify these costs?

Lastly, could you confirm that my personal information will be kept confidential during this process?

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Agnes
